          "reviewBody": "A good school have fair-minded, passionate, honest, well-mannered, inspirer skilled, and supportive mentors who have a strong positive impact on the student's attitude and personality. And teachers require so many positive qualities like care, compassion, patience and commitment. Class 5 teachers have all these qualities in abundance. Especially Mamta Arya Maam you’ve shown your commitment and love for our child and put in so much of your own time and effort to bring-out his best. By helping our son to develop his social skills and feel confident in your classroom, you have been exactly what we were looking for. We couldn’t be more thankful that we have had you in our lives.\nThank you so much for all this!",
